Author: SowoneulMalhaebwaa
Text: 100% true story about chunky purging. I was going out with some friends and I was underage so we pregamed at someone's house. However, I binged on a whole box of pasta with alfredo about an hour before. I got a text mid purge and had to book it to get to my friend's house. We start drinking and I get drunk really fast. We step outside for a cigarette and the cool air hits me and I just projectile vomit in the grass.   Then one of my lovely friends said "Damn do you even chew your food?" because they saw almost whole penne noodles in the grass. I was mortified and didn't know how to respond. It was the most embarrassing shit that ever happened.
